Package: AbNames
Type: Package
Title: Standardize Antibody Names
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Helen", "Lindsay", email = "helen.lindsay@chuv.ch", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8614-1661"))
Description: Provides functions for matching human antibody names, e.g. from an 
    antibody vendor website, to gene names using information from the Human
    Genome Naming Consortium (HGNC), NCBI, Ensembl, and the protein ontology.
    Also provides a data set of antibodies used in publically available
    CITE-seq experiments, and methods for standardising names using this
    reference.
